{"article_id":"lVYitABES21qheUl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"hopeful","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that a controversial Republican memo about the FBI might undermine the Russia investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"appeared poised Thursday to allow the document 's release .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"Trump and his aides signaled throughout the day","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"they would not use executive power","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"to block Congress from making the memo public ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"setting up a clash with the FBI and intelligence officials ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"who warn","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"the memo distorts facts","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"and could jeopardize intelligence-gathering information .","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"The document is said to allege","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"the FBI abused its surveillance tools .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Trump himself reviewed and read the memo on Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"White House officials told CNN ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and discussed it with chief of staff John Kelly and the White House counsel 's office .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Trump plans to tell Congress","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"he has no objections to the memo 's release ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"a senior administration official said on Thursday .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"In recent phone calls , Trump has told friends","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"he believes","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"the memo would expose bias within the FBI 's top ranks","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"and make it easier for him to argue","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the Russia investigations are prejudiced against him ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"according to two sources .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"As the debate rages","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"about whether the GOP memo is inaccurate and misleading","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"-- and whether it 's appropriate to reveal such classified intelligence at all --","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Trump appears to be more preoccupied with the political calculus .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"He views the memo as proof","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"the intelligence community was unfairly targeting him","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"and fodder for his ultimate goal","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"of bringing an end to the Russia investigation","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that he has dubbed a `` witch hunt , ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"sources said .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Many Republicans have backed Trump","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"in pushing for the memo 's release ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"though they deny","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"their motivations are related to the Russia investigation .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` If Americans ' civil liberties were abused ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"then that needs to come to light","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"so that does n't happen again , ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan said during a Republican retreat in West Virginia on Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"`` This memo is not an indictment of the FBI , of the Department of Justice ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"it does not impugn the Mueller investigation or the deputy attorney general . ''","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"His views were not shared by all Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Sens . Jeff Flake , R-Arizona , and John Thune , R-South Dakota , expressed misgivings","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"about releasing the information","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"contained in the document","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"publicly .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Meanwhile , some White House officials downplayed the memo 's significance ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"the facts","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"contained within the document","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"have already been reported .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The document was crafted by staff Republicans on the House Intelligence Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"led by Chairman Devin Nunes , a Trump ally .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Trump had a five-day window","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"to block the memo 's public release","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"after the House Intelligence Committee voted along party lines Monday to release it .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"The White House said","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"it was conducting a national security and legal review","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"before making a decision .","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"But it was n't clear what precise steps","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"-- if any --","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"the White House or Congress was taking","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"to ease the concerns of the FBI and intelligence officials over the memo 's content .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Before the House Intelligence Committee sent the memo to the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"the panel made certain changes to the document ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"though Republicans and Democrats on the committee differ on the number and substance of their alterations .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"Democrats say","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"there were five changes ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"while Republicans insist","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"there were only two .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"The changes prompted another spat between the leaders of the intelligence panel ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"with Democratic Rep. Adam Schiff insisting","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"lawmakers re-vote on the revised version .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"A source familiar with the process","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"of reviewing the memo","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"said","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"`` accommodations '' were made in response to concerns","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"aired over the past two days ,","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"though the source indicated","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"the steps were n't initiated by the White House .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"A White House official told reporters aboard Air Force One","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"that the memo would likely be made public with no redactions .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"`` We have had over the last couple days","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"to look at it","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"to make sure","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"it does n't give away too much in terms of classification , ''","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"the official said","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"as Trump was returning from West Virginia ,","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"where he addressed GOP lawmakers .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"`` Right now , I think","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"it will be that we tell the Congress , probably tomorrow ,","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"that the President is OK with it . ''","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"`` I doubt","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"there will be any redactions , ''","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"the official said .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"`` Then it is in Congress ' hands after that . ''","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"Whatever changes were made to the memo did not appear to placate the FBI ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"which had issued a rare public statement earlier in the week","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"expressing `` grave concerns '' over the memo 's public release .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"`` There may be editing of the text of this memo ,","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"but that does n't change the overall false narrative , ''","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"a US official familiar with the FBI stance said on Thursday .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"`` There are still grave concerns . ''","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"The President continues to seethe over the Justice Department 's handling of nearly everything Russia-related ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"sources said .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Recently , much of that anger has been directed toward his Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"who oversees Mueller and the Russia investigation .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Trump has told his associates and aides","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"he wants the memo released soon ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"believing","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"that it could discredit the agency","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"investigating possible collusion between his campaign associates and Russia .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"White House deputy press secretary Raj Shah denied on Thursday","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that the purpose of releasing the memo was to undermine the Mueller probe","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"and insisted","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that the White House is simply playing their role in a process","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"initiated by Congress .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"`` No , the purpose is transparency , ''","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Shah said ,","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"when asked by CNN about the effect on the Mueller investigation .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"`` This is a legislative process ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"they have initiated it .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"We are only following through on our role throughout the House rules . ''","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"On Wednesday , Trump was also upset in the wake of the FBI 's statement","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"challenging the release of the controversial memo .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"The FBI 's harshly worded statement was a rare public rebuke ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"all the more stinging","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"now that the bureau is led by Director Chris Wray ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"who Trump handpicked","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"after he fired James Comey last May .","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"In condemning the four-page memo","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"that alleges surveillance abuses on behalf of the FBI and Justice Department ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"the FBI said ,","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"`` we have grave concerns about material omissions of fact","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"that fundamentally impact the memo 's accuracy . ''","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"This follows a Justice Department statement","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"that warned","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"releasing the memo `` would be extraordinarily reckless . ''","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"The FBI 's statement was issued","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"just hours after the President made clear","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"he wanted the document public .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"People familiar with the President 's thinking say","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"the fate of Rosenstein , the deputy attorney general , remains in question amid the expected release of the Nunes memo .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"The document claims","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"the FBI abused the Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"( FISA )","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"when it used an opposition research dossier on Trump and Russia as part of its case","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"to obtain a highly classified warrant on former Trump campaign foreign policy adviser Carter Page ,","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"people familiar with the document say .","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"One person suggested","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"if Rosenstein merely submitted an application","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"to renew a FISA warrant","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"( one","depth":17},{"id":158,"text":"granted under previous leadership","depth":18},{"id":159,"text":"and based , in part , on information from the infamous dossier )","depth":18},{"id":160,"text":"that probably would n't be a damning enough revelation for Trump to move to fire Rosenstein .","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"But another person said","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"Trump is so frustrated with the Russia investigation and , in turn , Rosenstein","depth":15},{"id":163,"text":"that he may look for any opportunity","depth":16},{"id":164,"text":"to build a case for Rosenstein 's firing .","depth":16},{"id":165,"text":"He could argue","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"that Rosenstein failed to scrutinize the information","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"initially used","depth":17},{"id":168,"text":"to request the warrant","depth":17},{"id":169,"text":"and therefore did n't do his due diligence .","depth":15},{"id":170,"text":"These discussions are ongoing within the White House ,","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"one of the sources said .","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"Another source familiar with White House discussions said","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"they would be `` stunned ''","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"if anything happens to Rosenstein","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"even though he 's not a Trump favorite .","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"As CNN has previously reported ,","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"the President has vented recently about wanting to fire Rosenstein .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"But for now , it remains unclear whether he 's willing to take such an extraordinary step ,","depth":9},{"id":179,"text":"particularly given the backlash","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"he faced","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"after dismissing Comey .","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"JUST WATCHED Cooper to Rep. Nunes :","depth":5},{"id":183,"text":"You 've fooled us once","depth":5},{"id":184,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":5},{"id":185,"text":"MUST WATCH Cooper to Rep. Nunes :","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"You 've fooled us once","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"07:43","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"Trump 's top aides have been posturing on the memo","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"ever since the committee voted to approve the document 's release on Monday .","depth":7},{"id":190,"text":"Officials have been unable to say","depth":7},{"id":191,"text":"whether anyone inside the White House worked with Nunes or House Republicans on the document .","depth":7},{"id":192,"text":"After the House committee voted down party lines","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"to release the document ,","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"the memo was couriered to the White House on Monday evening","depth":8},{"id":195,"text":"and an interagency review process began on the contents of the controversial memo .","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"The memo was held in a room","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"designated for classified material .","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"especially those closely aligned with Trump in the House ,","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"have argued","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"the memo must be released","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"because it details abuse of power by law enforcement officials .","depth":7},{"id":203,"text":"But Democrats have said","depth":6},{"id":204,"text":"that memo is nothing more than an attempt by Nunes","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"-- who was a member of the executive committee","depth":10},{"id":206,"text":"leading Trump presidential transition team --","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"and other Republicans","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"to undercut special counsel Robert Mueller 's Russia investigation .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":417,"left":0,"right":416,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":416,"left":389,"right":415,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":389,"left":243,"right":388,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":243,"left":233,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":212,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":1,"right":211,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":211,"left":2